descriptionHtml:
Okay, this is just a small thing that I though was cute. I made a small pen in Solitude and put some hares in it. So yeah, kid of like a hare zoo. Compleately unneccesairy, but very cute and needfull! 
It\'s very easy to find. If you teleport to Solitude, just walk straight ahead past the \"market\" and you\'ll find it to your right (:

Please leave a comment if you find any buggs or know ways to make it better. I tried to make the hares less afraid of you, don\'t know if I succeded though, let me know (:

I updated the pen with some plants/trees (:
author: Miaouwsan
